text: The New Zealand Warriors are a New Zealand professional rugby league team. The team is based in Auckland, New Zealand. They were founded in 1995. They currently play in the National Rugby League competition. They have not won any premierships. They are the only non-Australian team in the NRL. ==Other websites== * Category:National Rugby League Category:Sports teams in New Zealand Category:Auckland Category:1995 establishments in Oceania Category:1990s establishments in New Zealand
